			<div class="horz-line"></div>
		</div>
		<div class="font-content info-section-details">
			<p>Several item types <strong>cannot</strong> receive bonus stats and cannot be flamed, namely:</p>
			<ul>
				<li class="list-items">Rings</li>
				<li class="list-items">Shoulderpads except <img src="/images/flames/flame-100.png"> Scarlet Shoulderpads</li>
				<li class="list-items">Emblems</li>
				<li class="list-items">Badges</li>
				<li class="list-items">Medals</li>
				<li class="list-items">Android & Android Hearts</li>
				<li class="list-items">Secondary Weapons (shield and katara included)</li>
			</ul>
			<p>When hovering over equipment, you may notice that on the top left corner of the zoomed-in item, certain items have transparent dots, while others have white dots. Any flame can be used on items with a transparent dot, while only non-level restricted flames can be used on items with a white dot.</p>

			<p>The table below describes each item type and several examples of items in each category. Mouse over each item image to see the item name.</p>
